M||name|cicd-dp
M||desc|dv's vc dpl management skill for yv. Covers preview vs. production dp workflow, environment variable management, dp hooks, maxDuration config, rollback procedures, and vc-specific nx.js 15 constraints.
M||vers|1.0.0
M||tx|---
M|Purp|tx|yv deploys to vc. Deployments are not trivial â€” wrong environment variables in production, incorrect `maxDuration` config on scraper rt, or a broken bd that deploys silently can take down the dashboard for both vt. This skill defines the dp discipline dv applies to every yv dpl.
