M|Roll|If a|
M|Roll|tx|```
M|Roll|tx|1. vc dashboard â†’ Deployments â†’ select last working dp â†’ "Redeploy"
M|Roll|tx|â†’ This is the fastest rollback â€” vc keeps all previous builds
M|Roll|2. I|up in vc dashboard â†’ redeploy
M|Roll|3. I|roll back migration (see rj's migration-management skill)
